and&lt;br /&gt;database schema design considered a plus&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Experience with Salesforce.com&lt;br /&gt;Mobile applications, e.g. Salesforce Touch or Salesforce 1 is a plus&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Experience with Salesforce&lt;br /&gt;Marketing Cloud products like Radian6, Exact Target, or Pardot considered a&lt;br /&gt;plus&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Experience with payments&lt;br /&gt;technology and industry is a plus&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Experience working with Oracle and&lt;br /&gt;DB2 databases is a plus&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with Big Data&lt;br /&gt;technology and concepts is a plus&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Ability to think abstractly and&lt;br /&gt;deal with ambiguous/under-defined problems&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;BS in computer science, computer&lt;br /&gt;engineering or equivalent work experience&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;American&lt;br /&gt;Express is an equal opportunity employer and makes employment decisions without&lt;br /&gt;regard to race, color, religion, sex, national origin, sexual orientation,&lt;br /&gt;gender identity, protected veteran status, disability status, or any other&lt;br /&gt;status protected by law. Click here to view the &lt;a href="http://www.dol.gov/ofccp/regs/compliance/posters/ofccpost.htm" rel="nofollow" rel="nofollow"&gt;EEO is the Law&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;poster. If the link does not work, please copy and paste the following URL in a&lt;br /&gt;new browser window: &lt;a href="http://www.dol.gov/ofccp/regs/compliance/posters/ofccpost.htm" rel="nofollow" rel="nofollow"&gt;http://www.dol.gov/ofccp/regs/compliance/posters/ofccpost.htm&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;p&gt;Offer of employment with&lt;br /&gt;American Express is conditioned upon the successful completion of a background&lt;br /&gt;verification check, subject to applicable laws and regulations.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;ReqID: 15010799', 'New York, NY', 'http://careers.stacko