ion, Minneapolis has the most Fortune 500 companies per capita, four beautiful seasons, and a variety of cultural and sports events. Our mission is to research and create futuristic products that will change the face of retail. We&amp;rsquo;re like a start-up with the resources of a big company to help you succeed and make a huge impact. We work with cool and emerging technologies to revolutionize the retail world! What does it mean to be &amp;ldquo;Minnesota nice&amp;rdquo;? Find out what engineers are talking about!', 'Minneapolis, MN', 'http://careers.stackoverflow.com/jobs/99911/software-engineer-intern-target', 'Thu, 08 Oct 2015 16:02:01 Z', '2015-10-08T16:02:01Z', 410);
