a variety of modern programming languages (Java, C/C++, Objective C, Python) and open-source technologies (Linux, SQLite, OpenGL, Spring, Hibernate)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;br /&gt;	&lt;li&gt;Experience developing cloud software services and an understanding of design for scalability, performance and reliability&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br /&gt;	&lt;li&gt;Development experience defining, developing and maintaining web service API&amp;#39;s&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br /&gt;	&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to mentor other software developers to maintain architectural vision and software quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br /&gt;	&lt;li&gt;Excellence in technical communications with both technical and non technical peers&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;', 'Gdask, Polska', 'http://careers.stackoverflow.com/jobs/99830/software-development-engineer-amazon-echo-java-amazon', 'Wed, 07 Oct 2015 20:02:02 Z', '2015-10-07T20:02:02Z', 128);
