trong&gt;Perks:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Heres a peek at some of the many perks youll enjoy:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;	&lt;li&gt;A great work environmentits never boring here, trust us.&lt;/li&gt;	&lt;li&gt;Werea family - lunches for birthdays, holiday parties, team outings, movie days, etc.&lt;/li&gt;	&lt;li&gt;Collaborationideas and input are always welcome&lt;/li&gt;	&lt;li&gt;Casual dressno suit, no tie, no problem!&lt;/li&gt;	&lt;li&gt;Health and dental&lt;/li&gt;	&lt;li&gt;Paid vacation and holidays&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;', 'Fairport, NY', 'http://careers.stackoverflow.com/jobs/99767/front-end-developer-sharp-notions-llc', 'Wed, 07 Oct 2015 14:02:02 Z', '2015-10-07T14:02:02Z', 967);
