software; we need you to help contribute.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;p&gt;You will be a key part in accurately estimating the timing of software delivery.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;REQUIREMENTS:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;p&gt;Bachelors Degree in Computer Science, Software Engineering or related field, Masters preferred&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;p&gt;Expert knowledge of Java (7+ years)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;p&gt;Strong understanding of modern unit testing and version control - SVN or Git preferred&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;p&gt;Familiar with Agile software development methodologies&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;p&gt;Interested in working for a fast paced tech and product oriented company&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;p&gt;GrubHub Holdings Inc.&amp;nbsp;is an EQUAL EMPLOYMENT OPPORTUNITY/AFFIRMATIVE ACTION employer.&lt;/p&gt;', 'Chicago, IL', 'http://careers.stackoverflow.com/jobs/92270/senior-software-engineer-grubhub-inc', 'Sun, 04 Oct 2015 18:02:02 Z', '2015-10-04T18:02:02Z', 1818);
