taff or forums and other resources available to you as needed. &lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Log bugs with development team with clear and precise information, detailing the issue and how to reproduce.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Demonstrate an increasing level of customer care skills&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Weekend on-call coverage for production issues (once youve reached the appropriate experience level)&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Role is based during Eastern Standard Time or Central European Time&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;', 'Bengaluru, India', 'http://careers.stackoverflow.com/jobs/97736/l2-software-support-engineer-30k-crossover', 'Fri, 02 Oct 2015 21:02:02 Z', '2015-10-02T21:02:02Z', 2161);
