mp;ldquo;user&amp;rdquo; is a real person with a severe health condition. The work we are doing is incredibly exciting because the impact we can have is massive, but it also requires extra care and increased responsibility to ensure every decision we make reflects this understanding.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'Chicago, IL', 'http://careers.stackoverflow.com/jobs/96905/senior-full-stack-engineer-triggr-health', 'Fri, 02 Oct 2015 20:02:02 Z', '2015-10-02T20:02:02Z', 2229);
